return ['messages'=>['<h3>Want to see what\'s new? <br>Head to JCK and explore our latest collection!</h3>'=>'<h3>想了解最新信息吗？  <br>前往 JCK 探索我们的最新系列！</h3>','<h5>Consistent quality</h5>
<p>CNC technology consistently yields high-quality products with the same level of precision manufacturing.</p>'=>'<h5>质量稳定</h5>
<p>数控技术始终以相同的制造精度生产出高质量的产品。</p>','<h5>Greater precision</h5>
<p>CNC technology ensures that each piece meets your specifications exactly, reducing the likelihood of errors or rework.</p>'=>'<h5>精度更高</h5>
<p>数控技术可确保每件产品都完全符合您的规格要求，从而减少出错或返工的可能性。</p>','<h5>Increased design flexibility</h5>
<p>CNC technology allows us to create custom pieces that are truly unique and personalized while meeting stringent deadlines.</p>'=>'<h5>提高设计灵活性</h5>
<p>数控技术使我们能够在严格的期限内制作出真正独一无二的个性化定制产品。</p>','<p><big><span class="trx_addons_accent"><strong>2</strong></span></big></p>
<p>Improved efficiency and productivity in the manufacturing process, enhancing the ability to meet customer demand in a timely and cost-effective manner. </p>'=>'<p><big><span class="trx_addons_accent"><strong>2</strong></span></big></p>
<p>提高生产过程的效率和生产力，增强及时满足客户需求的能力，提高成本效益。  </p>','<p><big><span class="trx_addons_accent"><strong>3</strong></span></big></p>
<p>Ability to create custom pieces more easily and with greater accuracy, giving us a competitive edge in the market, and better fulfilling our customers’ needs.</p>'=>'<p><big><span class="trx_addons_accent"><strong>3</strong></span></big></p>
<p>能够更轻松、更准确地定制产品，使我们在市场上更具竞争优势，并更好地满足客户的需求。</p>','<p><big><span class="trx_addons_accent">CNC technology</span></big> allows for the creation of precise and complex shapes and designs out of metal. It stands for "Computer Numerical Control". <span class="trx_addons_inverse">Think of it as a robot that follows a set of programmed instructions to make something very small and detailed.</span> In the jewellery industry, CNC machines can be used to create a wide range of jewellery pieces, from simple wedding bands to intricate, multi-layered designs. As a bespoke manufacturing jeweller, CNC technology acts as a powerful complement – not a replacement – to our decades of experience and craftsmanship. It provides our masters with a new range of tools for jewellery production.</p>'=>'<p><big><span class="trx_addons_accent">数控技术</span></big>数控技术可以用金属制作出精确、复杂的形状和设计。它是 "计算机数控 "的缩写。   <span class="trx_addons_inverse">把它想象成一个机器人，按照一组程序指令来制作非常小而精细的东西。</span> 在珠宝行业，数控机床可用于制作各种珠宝首饰，从简单的结婚戒指到复杂的多层设计，不一而足。作为定制珠宝制造商，数控技术是对我们数十年经验和工艺的有力补充，而不是替代。它为我们的大师提供了一系列新的珠宝生产工具。  </p>','<p><span class="trx_addons_accent"><strong><big>1</big></strong></span></p>
<p>Greater precision and accuracy in the creation of jewellery pieces, especially for intricate filigree work or small pave-set stones.</p>'=>'<p><span class="trx_addons_accent"><strong><big>1</big></strong></span></p>
<p>在制作珠宝首饰时，尤其是在制作复杂的花丝工艺或镶嵌小宝石时，能获得更高的精确度和准确性。</p>','<p><span class="trx_addons_tiny_text">The contrasting shades of yellow and white gold intertwine harmoniously, creating a captivating interplay of colors. </span></p>'=>'<p><span class="trx_addons_tiny_text">对比鲜明的黄金和白金色调和谐交织，创造出迷人的色彩交织效果。  </span></p>','<p><span class="trx_addons_tiny_text">The smoothness of the cuts and the crispness of the edges highlight the attention to detail and artistry that went into creating this <small>stunning</small> piece.</span></p>'=>'<p><span class="trx_addons_tiny_text">平滑的切割和清晰的边缘彰显了制作这款<small>令人惊叹的</small>作品对细节和艺术的关注。</span></p>','<p><strong><span class="trx_addons_accent">Date &amp; Time</span></strong><br /><span class="trx_addons_accent">2-4 Jun (Fri-Sun) 0930-1800</span><br /><span class="trx_addons_accent">5 Jun (Mon) 0930-1630</span></p><p><strong><span class="trx_addons_accent">Booth 53107, Level 1, Hong Kong Pavilion<br /></span></strong><strong style="font-size: 16px; background-color: var(--theme-color-bg_color); color: var(--theme-color-text); letter-spacing: 0px;"><span class="trx_addons_accent">The Venetian Expo, Las Vegas, Nevada</span></strong></p>'=>'<p><strong><span class="trx_addons_accent">日期和时间</span></strong><br><span class="trx_addons_accent">6 月 2-4 日（周五-周日） 0930-1800</span><br><span class="trx_addons_accent">6 月 5 日（周一） 0930-1630</span></p><p><strong><span class="trx_addons_accent">香港馆 1 层 53107 号展位<br></span></strong><strong style="font-size: 16px; background-color: var(--theme-color-bg_color); color: var(--theme-color-text); letter-spacing: 0px;"><span class="trx_addons_accent">内华达州拉斯维加斯威尼斯人世博会</span></strong></p>','<p>CNC technology can greatly benefit jewellery manufacturing in the following ways:</p>'=>'<p>数控技术可在以下方面为珠宝制造带来极大益处：</p>','<p>For centuries, jewellery making has long been a beautiful handcraft rooted in tradition, skills, and artistry. Without question, as a creative jewellery manufacturer in the industry, we recognize the importance of being innovative. Over the years, we have developed different production techniques, and one that stands out is <span class="trx_addons_accent">computer numerical control (CNC) technology</span> for fine jewellery manufacturing production. Today, we would like to introduce this innovative technique, which is renowned for its precision and beauty.</p>'=>'<p>几个世纪以来，珠宝制作一直是植根于传统、技能和艺术的精美手工艺。毫无疑问，作为业内富有创造力的珠宝制造商，我们认识到创新的重要性。多年来，我们开发了不同的生产技术，其中最突出的就是用于高级珠宝制造生产的<span class="trx_addons_accent">计算机数控（CNC）技术</span>。今天，我们要介绍的就是这项以精确和美观著称的创新技术。   </p>','<p>While traditional handcrafted jewellery remains valued, CNC technology<span class="trx_addons_accent"> offers</span><span class="trx_addons_dark trx_addons_accent"> u</span><span class="trx_addons_accent">nprecedented capabilities for precision, complexity, creativity, and efficiency</span> in our manufacturing production. As an innovative jewellery manufacturer, we are committed to staying ahead of the curve when it comes to technology and innovation to provide our B2B customers with the best possible service and products.</p><p><a href="https://x4v3b03dwm-staging.onrocket.site/contact-us/">Contact us</a> today to learn more about our B2B jewellery services and how we can create unique, high-quality, and personalized jewellery pieces that perfectly match your needs.</p>'=>'<p>虽然传统手工珠宝仍然受到重视，但数控技术为我们的制造生产<span class="trx_addons_accent"> 提供了</span><span class="trx_addons_accent">前所未有的精确性、复杂性、创造性和效率</span>。作为一家创新型珠宝制造商，我们致力于在技术和创新方面保持领先，为我们的 B2B 客户提供最好的服务和产品。 </p><p>现在就<a href="https://x4v3b03dwm-staging.onrocket.site/zh-hans/%e8%81%94%e7%b3%bb%e6%88%91%e4%bb%ac/">联系我们</a>，进一步了解我们的 B2B 珠宝服务，以及我们如何为您打造独一无二、高品质和个性化的珠宝作品，完美满足您的需求。</p>','Benefits of CNC technology?'=>'数控技术的优势？','Book Your Appointment'=>'预约','Divider'=>'分割器','How CNC technology enhances our B2B service?'=>'数控技术如何提升我们的 B2B 服务？','What is CNC technology?'=>'什么是 CNC 技术？','editor-text-editor-1456f44'=>'<p><span class="trx_addons_tiny_text">平滑的切割和清晰的边缘彰显了制作这款<small>令人惊叹的</small>作品对细节和艺术的关注。</span></p>','editor-text-editor-36be40b'=>'<p>虽然传统手工珠宝仍然受到重视，但数控技术为我们的制造生产<span class="trx_addons_accent"> 提供了</span><span class="trx_addons_accent">前所未有的精确性、复杂性、创造性和效率</span>。作为一家创新型珠宝制造商，我们致力于在技术和创新方面保持领先，为我们的 B2B 客户提供最好的服务和产品。 </p><p>现在就<a href="https://x4v3b03dwm-staging.onrocket.site/zh-hans/%e8%81%94%e7%b3%bb%e6%88%91%e4%bb%ac/">联系我们</a>，进一步了解我们的 B2B 珠宝服务，以及我们如何为您打造独一无二、高品质和个性化的珠宝作品，完美满足您的需求。</p>','editor-text-editor-44cddf6'=>'<p><big><span class="trx_addons_accent"><strong>2</strong></span></big></p>
